text: Schicklgruber is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Alois Schicklgruber, better known as Alois Hitler, Austrian civil servant and the father of Adolf Hitler *Josef Schicklgruber (born 1967), Austrian footballer *Maria Schicklgruber (1795–1847), the paternal grandmother of Adolf Hitler ==See also== *Hitler family
title: Schicklgruber
